Minotor is a MIDI-controlled LED matrix software.

License:
Minotor is released under GPL but embedded RtMidi¹ and QExtSerialPort². Also, I don´t know the license of art³.

[1] http://www.music.mcgill.ca/~gary/rtmidi/
[2] http://code.google.com/p/qextserialport/
[3] https://github.com/ohm2013loc/art

Building information:
http://wiki.minotor.org/doku.php/linux?DokuWiki=1gbk7vt1jkkm1fkv0pk5rqhao1
